arStrings.szText: That pit…I’ve been down there so long I could barely tell friend from foe. Glad I didn’t kill you.

You bested me. By the law of my people and the law of the Worm, I am yours to butcher and devour. But before that happens, I must put two cannibal chieftains under my knife. Grelkar the Craven and Zolmog Venomblood must die.
Because they banished me! Because they wounded my honor! Because I don’t like them! I need help to destroy them, wanderer.
